scripts.compile: tsc -p . && cp src/*.json build/src && cp -r test/fixtures build/test
scripts.compile-iam-protos: pbjs -t json google/iam/v1/iam_policy.proto google/iam/v1/options.proto google/iam/v1/policy.proto google/iam/v1/logging/audit_data.proto -p ./protos > protos/iam_service.json && pbjs -t static-module google/iam/v1/iam_policy.proto google/iam/v1/options.proto google/iam/v1/policy.proto google/iam/v1/logging/audit_data.proto -p ./protos > protos/iam_service.js && pbts protos/iam_service.js -o protos/iam_service.d.ts
scripts.compile-operation-protos: pbjs -t json google/longrunning/operations.proto -p ./protos > protos/operations.json && pbjs -t json google/rpc/status.proto google/rpc/error_details.proto google/protobuf/any.proto -p ./protos > protos/status.json && pbjs -t static-module google/longrunning/operations.proto -p ./protos > protos/operations.js && pbts protos/operations.js -o protos/operations.d.ts
scripts.prelint: cd samples; npm link ../; npm install
scripts.prepare: npm run compile && node ./build/tools/prepublish.js && mkdirp build/protos && cp -r protos/* build/protos/
scripts.samples-test: cd samples/ && npm link ../ && npm test && cd ../
